gantt
    title Voyage to Treasure Island
    dateFormat  YYYY-MM-DD

    section Preparation
    Recruit crew           :a1, 2024-01-01, 7d
    Provision ship         :a2, after a1, 5d
    Study treasure map     :a3, 2024-01-01, 10d
    Repair hull            :a4, after a1, 4d

    section Voyage Out
    Sail to open waters    :b1, after a2, 3d
    Navigate by stars      :b2, after b1, 14d
    Survive storm          :crit, b3, after b2, 2d
    Reach island           :b4, after b3, 1d

    section Treasure Hunt
    Scout the island       :c1, after b4, 2d
    Decode map clues       :c2, after c1, 3d
    Dig for treasure       :crit, c3, after c2, 2d
    Load treasure          :c4, after c3, 1d

    section Return
    Set sail home          :d1, after c4, 14d
    Evade Navy patrol      :crit, d2, after d1, 3d
    Arrive at port         :d3, after d2, 1d
    Divide the loot        :milestone, after d3, 0d